{"tid":54518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警平安夜醉駕　途人揭發走唔甩","createTime":"2016-12-25T15:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T16:19:36.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a73473861b495f3aeb1eafa49bd2d2212f53bf2","tid":54518,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"12月25日(日) 17:19更新 17:07建立   <br />\n<br />\n休班警涉嫌酒後駕駛，在木橋頭村被捕。(資料圖片)<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=inXPCrULM1zxCKPcBZ3uEBpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=ed948fd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】姓胡(47歲)休班警員，昨晚11時許，駕駛私家車進入元朗僑興路木橋頭村，期間一名姓胡(38歲)途人發現私家車不穩定行駛，遂報警求助，案件原列發現可疑人士處理。 <br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查，發現胡未能通過酒精呼氣測試，以涉嫌酒後駕駛將他拘捕，他其後已獲准保釋候查，須於明年1月下旬向警方報到。 <br />\n<br />\n警隊重申非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"ead8bc2f3411a30f5dcddd92a1fb14e24e0f4072","tid":54518,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"本星期排名<br />\n<br />\n1ST 新界北 +2 <br />\n2ND 水警+總部 +1 <br />\n3RD 新界南 0<br />\n4TH 西九龍 0<br />\n5TH 東九龍 0<br />\n6TH 港島 0<br />\n<br />\n前3位,可以參與亞洲休班警冠軍盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdafd0ed08d329d84c6b2f45b526143e9631977b","tid":54518,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:15:22.000Z","msg":"邊條友做嘅，做好市民係啱㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb756a6416df68a9b46428621bee5f4d75418895","tid":54518,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56a74d463693451713903d5fcd8d1398da4b6bc","tid":54518,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"